array.note: f[i] is the frequency of the ith radio-link
p[i] is the polarization of the ith radio-link

var.note: k is the relaxation level to be optimized

array.note: v1[q] is 1 iff the qth pair of radioelectric compatibility constraints is violated when relaxing another level
v2[q] is the number of times the qth pair of radioelectric compatibility constraints is violated when relaxing more than one level
d[i] is the distance between the ith pair of linked frequencies
